---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SolidComponent from '../components/solid.tsx';

import Projects from "../components/ProjectsFull.astro";

import { colorVariants } from "../colors.ts"
const colorVariant = [
  //"blue",
  //"green",
  "orange",
  "yellow",
][ Math.floor(Math.random()*(2)) ]
console.log(colorVariant);
---

<Layout title="Yash Karthik" description="Essays and short stories by Yash Karthik." showBars={false} route="/" colorVariant={colorVariant}>
  <main class="my-7 flex flex-col gap-0 flex-grow">

    <section class="
      self-center m-5
      max-w-none lg:w-7/12 md:w-8/12 sm:w-9/12 w-10/12
    ">
      <p class="text-4xl font-serif-styled">Hi, I'm Yash Karthik.</p> <br/>

      <p>Right now, I'm:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
        <li>Learning PCB design and trying to fabricate my own board.</li>

        <li>
          Writing code at
          <a target="_blank" href="https://helicone.ai/" class={`
            underline decoration-2
            ${colorVariants[colorVariant].decorationColor}
            underline-offset-2
          `}>Helicone</a> and living in SF (say hi if you're around).
        </li>

        <li>
          Studying computer engineering at
          <a target="_blank" href="https://ece.engineering/" class={`
            underline decoration-2
            ${colorVariants[colorVariant].decorationColor}
            underline-offset-2
          `}>Waterloo</a>.
        </li>
      </ul> <br/>

      <p>Before that, I have:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
        <li>Shipped semi-viral web apps built using ai apis.</li>

        <li>
          Written firmware for
          <a target="_blank" href="https://www.uwarg.com/" class={`
            underline decoration-2
            ${colorVariants[colorVariant].decorationColor}
            underline-offset-2
          `}>drones</a>.
        </li>

        <li>Run linux on lego ev3.</li>
      </ul> <br/>

      <p>Some lore:</p>
      <p class="p-5">
        <i>Five years ago I awoke in a strange new world: I learned to code. <br/><br/>
        My friend and I were tasked with cleaning-up the robotics lab after a late night session.
        Rather than spending hours sorting the parts manually, we built a robot to do it for us
        (finishing the task in a few days instead of hours xD).
        
        I knew how transformative technology is. It had been all around us. But actually leveraging
        it myself to automate a mundane task was when I truly <b>grokked</b> the power of technology.
        
        Since then, I've built fast and beautiful web apps; efficient and powerful robots; slow and
        clunky(?) VMs; and learned to embrace the lightness of being a <b>perpetual beginner</b>.</i>
      </p>
    </section>

    <Projects colorVariant={colorVariant}/>

    <section class="
      self-center m-5 mt-12
      max-w-none lg:w-7/12 md:w-8/12 sm:w-9/12 w-10/12
    ">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif-styled">Other/Fun</h2>
      <p class="italic my-2">stay whimsical</p>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
        <li>
          I like writing. While most of what I write is pure yap, I think I did justice to 
          <a target="_blank" href="https://yashkarthik.github.io/quartz" class={`
            underline decoration-2
            ${colorVariants[colorVariant].decorationColor}
            underline-offset-2
            `}>linear algebra
          </a> last term.
        </li>

        <li>I love drawing the side profile of cars! - one of the few things I can actually draw.</li>

        <li>
          Like many before me, I have wasted countless hours <i>ricing</i> my computer. Here's my
          <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/yashkarthik/dots" class={`
            underline decoration-2
            ${colorVariants[colorVariant].decorationColor}
            underline-offset-2
            `}>config
          </a>.
        </li>


        <li>I think my laptop skin is pretty cool.</li>
      </ul> <br/>

      <div class="flex flex-row gap-4 mx-5">
        <img src="/laptop.jpeg" alt="Car" class="
          size-56 rounded-sm
          grayscale hover:grayscale-0
          transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out" />
        <img src="/car.jpeg" alt="Car" class="
          size-56 rounded-sm
          grayscale hover:grayscale-0
          transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out" />
      </div>

    </section>
  </main>

  <a target="_blank" href="https://socratica.info/" class="self-center">‚ÅÇ</a>

</Layout>
